Hyperledger项目：
 Hyperledger Fabric Hyperledger Sawtooth Hyperledger Composer  模型：
 Assets(资产)  一般定义方式：
 /** * A vehicle asset. */ asset Vehicle identified by vin { o String vin }  继承方式：
 /** * A car asset. A car is related to a list of parts */ asset Car extends Vehicle { o String model --&gt; Part[] Parts }  抽象方式：
 /** * An abstract Vehicle asset. */ abstract asset Vehicle identified by vin { o String vin }   Participants(参与者)
